00:33.800 --> 00:35.279
All aboard!

02:03.600 --> 02:05.352
All right, let's go.

02:10.800 --> 02:13.314
That's my main man Pierce
coming back from the war!

02:13.400 --> 02:14.469
Thank you! Thank you, man.

02:22.880 --> 02:24.632
Hey, what's happening, Jack?

02:39.960 --> 02:41.279
Private party.

02:42.640 --> 02:44.232
Pick another card.

02:48.320 --> 02:49.673
There you go!

02:51.200 --> 02:53.077
Oh, I see what you're saying.

02:54.080 --> 02:55.672
There we go!

02:58.440 --> 03:00.271
Damn it! Give me that shit.

03:01.680 --> 03:03.238
Party's over!

03:03.440 --> 03:04.873
Here we go. Move on out.

03:04.960 --> 03:07.474
Move on out.
Step out! Step out!

03:07.720 --> 03:09.756
Everybody out! Out!

03:10.240 --> 03:11.240
Let's go!

03:11.320 --> 03:13.550
I know you can hear me.
Get the fuck up and go!

03:13.640 --> 03:16.040
I don't care what you
do during the week. Get out!

03:17.800 --> 03:20.109
Party's over!
Let's get it moving!

03:20.200 --> 03:21.713
You know how this works!

03:21.800 --> 03:22.800
Says who?

03:24.640 --> 03:25.675
I'm sorry?

03:25.760 --> 03:27.352
Man, take a hike!

03:27.440 --> 03:29.556
Come in here
smelling like pig juice!

03:33.800 --> 03:36.109
Excuse me, miss.
Thank you so much.

03:36.320 --> 03:37.456
What'd you say?

03:37.480 --> 03:39.118
I ain't said anybody
talking... Hey, man!

03:42.040 --> 03:44.873
Come on, man! Let me go, man!
Let me go!

03:48.240 --> 03:49.912
Hold on a second.

03:51.000 --> 03:54.072
Get the fuck out!
Get out! Get out!

03:54.800 --> 03:56.438
How many times
you want me to say it?

03:56.520 --> 03:57.919
You're moving slow!

03:59.400 --> 04:00.833
Come on, man!

04:01.000 --> 04:02.638
Motherfuckers, man!

04:03.480 --> 04:05.391
Look, Frank, man.
The owner split.

04:05.480 --> 04:06.913
Man, I'm sorry,
but you got a room

04:07.000 --> 04:08.718
full of open warrants
in there. All right?

04:08.840 --> 04:11.991
Just make sure you search
the women, you lazy bastard.

04:13.160 --> 04:14.912
All right. Watch your eyes.

04:15.000 --> 04:16.000
Oh, shit!

04:18.360 --> 04:20.271
You know
that's not right, brother!

04:22.280 --> 04:23.429
No, no, no!

04:27.440 --> 04:28.919
We gotta go
through the front.

04:29.000 --> 04:31.468
What? You wanna take these
guys out in public, Sarge?

04:31.560 --> 04:33.437
We have no fucking option.

04:33.520 --> 04:34.953
Go tell them. Run.
All right.

04:36.960 --> 04:39.030
You dirty pig!
Get the fuck out of here.

04:41.000 --> 04:42.149
Anybody else?

04:42.320 --> 04:44.754
Why're we not moving?
You wanna go next?

04:44.840 --> 04:46.193
Out, out, out!

04:46.280 --> 04:47.936
All right,
party's over, folks. Let's go!

04:47.960 --> 04:49.439
You heard him.
Time to move out!

04:49.520 --> 04:51.272
Put your drinks down
and step out the door.

04:51.360 --> 04:53.776
I do not understand,
I thought I was very clear!

04:53.800 --> 04:55.199
Let's go! Come on!

04:55.280 --> 04:56.599
Out of here! Let's go!
Come on!

04:56.680 --> 04:57.696
Congratulations.

04:57.720 --> 04:59.950
Get the fuck out! How many times
I gotta say "Move out"?

05:00.040 --> 05:01.439
Let's go!

05:01.520 --> 05:03.795
I know your black asses
is faster than that.

05:03.880 --> 05:04.949
Go!

05:05.120 --> 05:07.236
Let's move! Come on!
Move! Let's go!

05:08.160 --> 05:09.991
On your feet!
Move it! Let's go!

05:12.480 --> 05:14.198
We're taking them out front.

05:14.360 --> 05:15.713
Out the front door!
Let's go! Now!

05:15.800 --> 05:16.840
Taking them out the front.

05:17.040 --> 05:18.393
Shit!

05:18.920 --> 05:19.920
Out the front!

05:21.880 --> 05:23.836
Guys, sir, both sides.

05:23.920 --> 05:26.354
Up against
the wall. Against the wall.

05:26.520 --> 05:27.919
Let's move it. Come on.

05:28.400 --> 05:29.400
Let's go!

05:32.760 --> 05:34.910
Here we go. Squad's here.

05:35.880 --> 05:38.155
If they're not resisting,
don't push them.

05:41.600 --> 05:42.919
Put it right there.

05:45.280 --> 05:46.920
Right here against the wall.

05:47.280 --> 05:48.554
Welcome home!

05:49.560 --> 05:50.675
Thank you, sir.

05:50.760 --> 05:52.557
Get out the way.
Get out the way!

05:52.840 --> 05:54.512
Hands where we can see them.

05:54.600 --> 05:56.192
We had to use the front door.

05:56.360 --> 05:58.590
Shit!
Make it a public display.

05:59.120 --> 06:00.599
I almost feel bad for them.

06:01.120 --> 06:02.951
We gotta get out of here.
Quickly.

06:03.280 --> 06:05.589
Let's go! Get them in!

06:05.800 --> 06:08.040
All right! Start
loading them up! Let's go!

06:09.800 --> 06:10.949
Okay, let's go!

06:12.960 --> 06:14.359
Look at this shit!

06:15.400 --> 06:17.550
Let's hurry!
Get it out of here!

06:17.880 --> 06:19.108
Get it out! Let's go!

06:23.120 --> 06:24.917
Make sure we get
those guys at the back.

06:25.080 --> 06:26.752
What are you doing down here
all the time?

06:31.960 --> 06:33.456
We gotta get this moving!

06:33.480 --> 06:34.549
Stop messing with us.

06:34.640 --> 06:35.868
These people
didn't do a thing.

06:35.960 --> 06:37.234
Where's the other one?

06:37.320 --> 06:39.072
It should be here any minute.

06:39.160 --> 06:40.309
What did they do?

06:40.440 --> 06:42.158
Please calm down!
Everything's fine.

06:44.560 --> 06:45.834
Finally!

06:50.920 --> 06:51.920
Over here.

06:52.080 --> 06:54.469
This is our neighborhood
and here y'all come.

06:54.680 --> 06:55.829
That's not necessary.

06:56.000 --> 06:57.149
Open the door! Get them in!

07:04.440 --> 07:05.839
Arrests for
a private gathering?

07:05.960 --> 07:07.359
That's police overreach!

07:07.520 --> 07:09.590
You got no liquor license
on this place.

07:09.680 --> 07:11.238
Get the fuck out of my face.

07:13.320 --> 07:15.675
Let's just keep it calm.
Are you fucking kidding me?

07:18.440 --> 07:21.637
Come on! Get in
the damn van! Step in there!

07:25.480 --> 07:26.515
Move, let's go!

07:27.000 --> 07:28.877
Let's get them moving,
gentlemen!

07:29.040 --> 07:31.952
Let's go!
Get them in the wagon!

07:33.160 --> 07:36.038
Hey, Dave! Told you you'd
get busted, you alcoholic!

07:36.280 --> 07:37.713
Oh, the night's not over!

07:40.200 --> 07:41.679
Go home!
Go home!

07:41.840 --> 07:42.989
Go home!

07:43.160 --> 07:44.388
You go home!

07:49.560 --> 07:51.480
- Get them in.
- Last one.

07:52.680 --> 07:53.874
Get them in!

07:54.040 --> 07:55.519
You punk-ass
motherfuckers!

07:59.720 --> 08:00.856
Let's go, get in!

08:00.880 --> 08:02.233
Don't touch me!

08:02.800 --> 08:04.233
Let's go! In!

08:04.400 --> 08:05.719
I'm moving!

08:05.920 --> 08:07.558
Get in! Let's go!

08:12.200 --> 08:13.758
Get in the car! Let's go!

08:41.280 --> 08:42.837
Check this, motherfuckers!

09:04.200 --> 09:06.111
Bub, can't even
ride that bike!

09:06.360 --> 09:08.641
You know good and well you don't
know how to ride no bike.

09:10.760 --> 09:12.432
Do it, man! Throw it!

09:12.600 --> 09:13.794
Catch this!

09:15.880 --> 09:17.950
Yeah! That's what
I'm talking about!

09:18.480 --> 09:20.277
It's show time now!

09:29.000 --> 09:31.296
Destroyers
striking from as far as three miles

09:31.320 --> 09:33.754
away from this
west side ghetto,

09:33.840 --> 09:36.149
where it all began
early this morning

09:36.240 --> 09:38.515
with a police raid on an
after-hours drinking parlor.

09:38.920 --> 09:41.150
There have been
some reports of gunfire.

09:41.240 --> 09:43.595
Police are under orders
not to fire.

09:43.680 --> 09:46.592
More than 200 looters
have been arrested so far.

09:46.680 --> 09:48.910
Police officials say they
do not have enough men

09:49.000 --> 09:50.433
to worry much
about the looters.

09:50.520 --> 09:52.670
They are there
to protect the firemen.

09:54.480 --> 09:56.357
But that is
why you elected me.

09:57.960 --> 09:59.188
To bring about change.

10:00.320 --> 10:02.959
But during this time,

10:03.160 --> 10:06.277
it's important that
we all settle down.

10:07.960 --> 10:10.030
- Settle yourself!
- I know you're angry.

10:10.120 --> 10:11.599
I'm angry, too.

10:11.680 --> 10:14.797
This city has problems,
especially with the policemen.

10:14.880 --> 10:15.949
We have problems.

10:17.600 --> 10:19.033
However,

10:19.600 --> 10:21.511
change doesn't
happen overnight.

10:21.720 --> 10:24.109
But change is coming.

10:25.280 --> 10:26.349
Let's work together!

10:26.440 --> 10:28.874
Nah! Bring Stokely Carmichael
down here!

10:29.040 --> 10:30.792
We don't wanna hear
from your ass!

10:30.960 --> 10:34.032
Look here.
This is what I need you to do!

10:34.200 --> 10:37.510
I need you to not mess up
your own neighborhood.

10:37.680 --> 10:39.238
This is your home!

10:39.400 --> 10:40.549
Yeah, burn it down!

10:40.720 --> 10:42.711
Burning it down
is not the answer!

10:44.480 --> 10:46.675
Burn it down! Burn it down!

10:49.800 --> 10:51.313
Settle down! Settle down!

10:58.200 --> 11:00.509
Hoses up! Hoses up!

11:00.720 --> 11:02.711
Get that engine
in a little closer!

11:03.360 --> 11:05.032
Engine four, let's relay!

11:05.200 --> 11:07.509
Come on! Roll it back!
You gotta roll it back.

11:08.920 --> 11:11.718
We gonna let
this motherfucker burn!

11:17.320 --> 11:18.355
What the fuck!

11:18.440 --> 11:20.000
Let's move back! Come on!

11:20.200 --> 11:21.679
Get out of here!

11:32.720 --> 11:34.576
At the
request of Mayor Cavanaugh,

11:34.600 --> 11:35.669
we've made state police

11:35.760 --> 11:37.193
and National
Guardsmen available

11:37.280 --> 11:40.590
to assist in dealing
with what is a case

11:40.720 --> 11:42.870
of lawlessness and hoodlumism

11:43.040 --> 11:45.349
and to protect
the persons and property

11:45.440 --> 11:47.795
of people
in the areas involved.

11:48.440 --> 11:50.351
Here in Detroit, a city of war

11:50.480 --> 11:52.038
where snipers
hide on rooftops,

11:52.120 --> 11:53.473
the violence continues.

11:53.560 --> 11:54.560
US Army paratroopers,

11:54.640 --> 11:56.710
National Guardsmen,
state and local police

11:56.800 --> 11:59.712
are continuing the fight
against a handful of snipers.

11:59.800 --> 12:04.396
On the city's west side, a 150-block
area is off-limits to everybody.

12:04.480 --> 12:08.234
This is no man's land, an area
of destruction and devastation.

12:08.320 --> 12:10.231
ABC newsman Tom Mclntyre says

12:10.320 --> 12:12.550
it's hard to believe that this
could happen in America.

12:12.640 --> 12:15.791
But here it is, in Detroit,
the nation's fifth largest city.

12:15.920 --> 12:18.559
I am declaring
a public state of emergency.

12:18.640 --> 12:22.758
And I am also indicating
that I will promulgate

12:22.840 --> 12:26.276
such rules,
orders and regulations

12:26.400 --> 12:29.472
as I deem necessary
to protect life and property.

12:33.920 --> 12:35.592
Second unit,
left lane!

12:35.760 --> 12:36.795
18-40!

12:39.960 --> 12:42.633
Rally point! Rally point A!

12:45.200 --> 12:47.270
Sniper in the window!

12:50.160 --> 12:51.639
Third floor window!

12:51.720 --> 12:53.551
Move to cover!
Move to cover now!

12:53.640 --> 12:55.835
Stand by! Hold your fire!

13:05.960 --> 13:08.190
Don't move!
All right, he's clear.

13:29.400 --> 13:30.719
Move back!

13:31.200 --> 13:32.200
Hey!

13:42.400 --> 13:44.152
Oh, I almost hit that one.

13:55.200 --> 13:57.509
There is no American right

13:57.600 --> 13:59.158
to loot stores

13:59.600 --> 14:01.113
or to burn buildings,

14:01.200 --> 14:03.395
or to fire rifles
from the rooftops.

14:04.280 --> 14:05.599
That is crime.

14:06.320 --> 14:08.959
And crime must be
dealt with forcefully

14:09.680 --> 14:12.194
and swiftly,
and certainly under law.

14:12.280 --> 14:13.696
...LBJ tell you

14:13.720 --> 14:15.676
that, "Violence never
accomplishes anything,

14:15.760 --> 14:17.216
"my fellow Americans."

14:17.240 --> 14:19.674
Don't you see,
the real problem with violence

14:19.760 --> 14:22.354
is that we have
never been violent.

14:22.440 --> 14:23.873
We have been too nonviolent!

14:41.600 --> 14:43.397
Excuse me!

14:44.560 --> 14:46.551
Go back
the way you came!

14:46.720 --> 14:48.296
I need to go down this road
to get to work.

14:48.320 --> 14:49.878
What did I say? Back!

14:49.960 --> 14:52.315
I need to go down this road
to get to work, Ford Assembly.

14:52.480 --> 14:53.913
Hold on! Where you going?

14:54.120 --> 14:55.758
Hey! Let him go!

14:57.280 --> 14:58.998
You cannot go this...

15:01.960 --> 15:03.960
Take cover!
We might have a sniper on...

15:05.400 --> 15:07.277
Boy, would you look at this.

15:07.800 --> 15:09.313
So sad.

15:10.080 --> 15:12.469
It's preventable, you know.
That's the worst part.

15:13.760 --> 15:15.440
Look at this.
This looks like fucking 'Nam.

15:15.480 --> 15:16.833
You believe this is the USA?

15:16.920 --> 15:18.319
And we're to blame.

15:20.920 --> 15:23.309
By standing by,
the trouble started. Now this.

15:27.680 --> 15:29.511
What can you do with this?

15:30.520 --> 15:31.589
They're crazy.

15:31.760 --> 15:34.991
They're not crazy. They know
exactly what they're doing.

15:35.200 --> 15:37.111
This is gonna
be worse than '43.

15:43.880 --> 15:46.440
No, we need to stop
failing these people.

15:46.520 --> 15:48.016
They're looking to us, and
we keep letting them down

15:48.040 --> 15:49.155
left, right, and center.

15:54.800 --> 15:56.438
Take this motherfucker
right here. Halt!

15:57.040 --> 15:58.359
Halt!

15:58.640 --> 15:59.675
Halt!

16:02.880 --> 16:04.199
Get back!

16:05.720 --> 16:07.016
- Stay off the street!
- Halt!

16:07.040 --> 16:08.040
Back up!

16:08.720 --> 16:09.720
Hey!

16:11.400 --> 16:12.549
Come here!

16:13.800 --> 16:14.835
Get back off the street!

16:25.200 --> 16:26.553
Hey, Phil! Come on!

16:26.720 --> 16:28.915
Hey, Phil!
Forget him! Come on!

16:31.000 --> 16:32.149
Fuck!

16:33.880 --> 16:36.155
You're not supposed to
shoot the looters anyway.

16:36.560 --> 16:38.073
Yeah.

16:39.240 --> 16:41.549
How the hell
are we supposed to stop them?

16:44.600 --> 16:46.750
What a fucking specimen, huh?

17:06.359 --> 17:07.588
Confound it!

17:07.760 --> 17:10.354
What... What are you doing
under there?

17:10.520 --> 17:13.079
I just live down the street.

17:13.560 --> 17:16.028
If you can go
get my wife Roberta?

17:16.119 --> 17:18.156
You want me to
call the ambulance?

17:18.240 --> 17:19.719
No, no police!

17:19.880 --> 17:21.551
Just, please, Roberta.

17:21.720 --> 17:22.789
Goodness!

17:24.119 --> 17:25.473
Get me Roberta.

17:28.600 --> 17:30.795
1,100 National Guardsmen

17:30.880 --> 17:32.393
have been rushed
into as many areas

17:32.480 --> 17:34.869
as they can cover,
protecting police.

17:34.960 --> 17:37.474
Looters carry off thousands
of dollars' worth of goods

17:37.600 --> 17:39.670
with a gay sort of leisure.

17:39.760 --> 17:42.069
Many negro shop owners
put up signs

17:42.160 --> 17:44.549
reading "Soul Brother"
to avoid damage.

17:44.640 --> 17:46.471
But the fire bombers
and looters

17:46.560 --> 17:47.675
are indiscriminate.

17:47.760 --> 17:48.856
Just cuff him to the chair.

17:48.880 --> 17:49.976
I'll get to him
when I get a second.

17:50.000 --> 17:51.616
Write your address
and your date of birth.

17:51.640 --> 17:52.834
Talk to him!

17:52.920 --> 17:54.120
Where am I supposed
to put him?

17:54.160 --> 17:55.912
I don't care. Take him
to your house!

17:56.000 --> 17:57.296
Let's move
these negroes out of here!

17:57.320 --> 17:58.469
There's no room!

18:00.600 --> 18:01.669
Sergeant!

18:02.680 --> 18:04.591
Homicide detectives
wanna have a word with you.

18:04.680 --> 18:05.736
Quit pushing! You got room

18:05.760 --> 18:07.079
for two more
in holding or not?

18:09.320 --> 18:10.958
Step back from
the goddamn counter!

18:11.120 --> 18:13.680
Come on, move!
Behind the door!

18:14.760 --> 18:16.671
Hey! Whose prisoner is this?

18:19.000 --> 18:20.638
Don't talk to me!

18:22.360 --> 18:23.679
For God's sake.

18:24.360 --> 18:25.960
Sit the fuck down
and shut up!

18:26.280 --> 18:28.840
Krauss, in here. I need you.

18:29.320 --> 18:30.514
Go, come on.

18:30.680 --> 18:32.033
Guys, come on. Out.

18:35.680 --> 18:37.079
I got a young black,

18:37.160 --> 18:39.720
shotgunned in the vicinity
of Virginia Park.

18:40.320 --> 18:43.357
Did I hear earlier
you shot a black guy?

18:43.520 --> 18:45.556
I missed, called it in.

18:46.200 --> 18:47.713
You missed?

18:48.800 --> 18:50.791
I might've clipped him.
He was real fast.

18:52.200 --> 18:54.668
Sit down, patrolman. Sit down.

18:59.520 --> 19:01.158
What's the hold up?

19:04.720 --> 19:06.256
Schools, city offices

19:06.280 --> 19:08.350
and many stores remain
closed today in Detroit,

19:08.440 --> 19:11.113
and a 9:00 p.m. curfew has
been ordered for this evening.

19:27.680 --> 19:28.715
Hey, Ma.

19:28.800 --> 19:29.835
Hey.

19:31.760 --> 19:33.079
I got it.

19:33.800 --> 19:34.915
Hello.

19:36.400 --> 19:37.753
No, I'm off.

19:38.520 --> 19:40.112
I worked a double.

19:42.280 --> 19:44.157
Okay. All right.

19:46.440 --> 19:47.668
What? Back to work?

19:47.760 --> 19:49.512
Yeah, Mr. LeFrank called.

19:49.680 --> 19:51.238
I thought Vinny
was your boss.

19:51.320 --> 19:53.356
I got two jobs,
two bosses, Ma.

19:53.440 --> 19:55.670
Security company needs me
for the looting.

19:55.880 --> 19:58.110
Looting?
Yeah, watch the news.

20:06.800 --> 20:09.872
Nowhere to run to, baby

20:10.560 --> 20:12.471
Nowhere to hide

20:13.800 --> 20:17.395
Got nowhere
to run to, baby

20:18.040 --> 20:19.519
Nowhere to hide

20:21.360 --> 20:24.397
It's not love
I'm running from

20:25.000 --> 20:28.151
It's the heartbreak
I know will come

20:28.320 --> 20:29.673
What do you say there, Fred?
Hey.

20:29.840 --> 20:30.875
Yo, you're late.

20:31.000 --> 20:32.616
Listen, I almost lost my job
getting here. I'm sorry.

20:32.640 --> 20:34.551
I don't give a damn
about Ford Motor Company.

20:34.640 --> 20:36.216
Bumper cars and sheet metal
motherfucker?

20:36.240 --> 20:37.440
You about to be
with the stars!

20:37.480 --> 20:39.675
But I need to
buy bread, negro.

20:42.640 --> 20:45.154
Listen, it's gonna be good.

20:46.880 --> 20:47.915
You sure?

20:48.000 --> 20:49.000
Yeah.

20:50.160 --> 20:51.160
All right?

20:52.000 --> 20:53.672
Thanks, man.
Yeah.

20:53.840 --> 20:55.831
I need you here, man.
I'm here!

20:56.000 --> 20:58.150
What you need?
Water or something?

20:58.360 --> 20:59.918
I know
you're no good for me

21:01.840 --> 21:03.910
