a solid guy though.

02:03:39.000 --> 02:03:40.274
Really.

02:04:35.200 --> 02:04:37.555
They know
what they're supposed to do.

02:04:48.840 --> 02:04:50.956
Jury entering. All rise.

02:04:58.600 --> 02:05:00.192
